definitions.definition: One of the female ( feminine ) sex or gender .

subdefinitions.definition: A human of the feminine sex.
An animal of the sex that produces eggs .
A plant which produces only that kind of reproductive organ capable of developing into fruit after impregnation or fertilization ; a pistillate plant.

definitions.definition: A bacterium which lacks the F factor , and is able to receive DNA from another bacterium which has that factor.
A female connector , pipe fitting, etc.
